# Entity

## Person

### Attribute

| name | type     | multiplicity |
|------+----------+--------------|
| id   | entityid | 1            |
| name | name     | 1            |

### Event

#### person.created
- category :: ActionEvent
- kind :: created
- selector :: source=crm
- actionName :: person.sync
- priority :: 0

#### person.updated
- category :: ActionEvent
- kind :: updated
- selector :: source=crm
- actionName :: person.sync
- priority :: 1

#### order.shipped
- category :: ActionEvent
- kind :: shipped
- priority :: 0

#### audit.ingested
- category :: ActionEvent
- kind :: ingested
- actionName :: audit.handle
- priority :: 0
